TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT s2.snap_id ,s2.model_typ_cd ,s2.period_id ,s2.run_mode_cd ,s1.max_snap_apc_typ_cd ,s2.req_run_ts ,s2.REQ_RUN_TM_UPDT_TS ,s2.REQ_RUN_TM_UPDT_ID ,s2.CORP_CD FROM (SELECT corp_cd ,model_typ_cd ,period_id ,run_mode_cd ,max(snap_apc_typ_cd) max_snap_apc_typ_cd FROM vrap.tsnap GROUP BY corp_cd ,model_typ_cd ,period_id ,run_mode_cd) s1 ,vrap.tsnap s2 WHERE s2.SNAP_RUN_STAT_CD = 1 -- pending only AND s2.req_run_ts < CURRENT TIMESTAMP + 15 MINUTES -- run time in past AND s1.CORP_CD = s2.CORP_CD AND s1.MODEL_TYP_CD = s2.MODEL_TYP_CD AND s1.PERIOD_ID = s2.PERIOD_ID AND s1.RUN_MODE_CD = s2.RUN_MODE_CD WITH UR

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: PERIOD_ID_lock = PERIOD_ID AND MODEL_TYP_CD_lock = MODEL_TYP_CD AND CORP_CD_lock = CORP_CD
